sentence: how much is a flight from washington to montreal
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.fare_id||'"', '"'||v2.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.airport_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0, flight_fare v1,
 flight v2, airport_service v3, city v4, airport_service v5,
 city v6 
WHERE ((v0.fare_id = ANY v1.fare_id) AND ((v1.flight_id = ANY v2.flight_id) 
AND (((v2.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) AND (v4.city_name = 'WASHINGTON'))) 
AND ((v2.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) AND (v6.city_name = 'MONTREAL'))))));
